<br>
<a name="Save"></a>It is important to save the configuration settings in the location different from the default one (normally this is a folder inside your local file system: <i><a href="mk:@MSITStore:help.chm::/language/customize/OVfile/UserFolder.htm" target="_parent">User folder</a>), as the <span class="UI_COMMAND" id="MenuBar_Empty_Tools.msg+MenuBar_Empty_Tools+7807">Reset</span> operation removes all the existing configuration files from the above mentioned default location.</td>
</tr>
</table>

